OL,6,FA care home worker has been jailed
OL,7,Fafter stealing money from a vulnerable
OL,8,Felderly resident.
OL,10,FFiona Le Clercq, 40, used the victim's
OL,11,Fbank card to withdraw a total of
OL,12,F#7,500 in 25 separate ATM transactions
OL,13,Fbetween mid-February and the end of
OL,14,FMarch 2023.
OL,16,FMs Le Clercq was sentenced to nine
OL,17,Fmonths in prison and ordered to pay
OL,18,Fback the money by the island's
OL,19,FMagistrates Court.
